British Land May Buy U.K. Properties for $281 Million, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-06T00:48:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-06/british-land-may-buy-u-k-properties-for-281-million-ft-says.html
British Land Co. is in advanced
discussions with  Societe Generale (GLE)  SA about buying a 175 million-
pound ($281 million) portfolio of U.K. properties which are
occupied by Virgin Active health clubs, the Financial Times
reported, without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 